# Drug Inventory and Supply Chain Tracking System - Backend

## Overview
This is the backend part of the Drug Inventory and Supply Chain Tracking System. It is designed to handle the server-side logic, manage database operations, and provide an API for the frontend to interact with.

## Prerequisites
- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) (v14 or later recommended)
- [npm](https://www.npmjs.com/) (comes with Node.js)

## Setup

1. **Clone the Repository**
   ```bash
   git clone <repository-url>
   cd backend

2. **Install dependencies**
   npm install

3. **Configure Environment Variables**
   DB_HOST=localhost
   DB_USER=root
   DB_PASSWORD=password
   DB_NAME=drug_inventory
   PORT=3000

4. **Run the Application**
   node app.js